		"description": "<p><em>Defensive (Light), Finesse</em></p>\n<p>You gain a +3 bonus to attack and damage rolls made with this magic sword. While you are attuned to the sword and use it to attack a fiend or undead, on a hit it deals an extra 2d10 radiant damage. In addition, while drawn the sword creates an aura in a 10-foot radius around you. You and friendly creatures in the aura gain&nbsp;<span class=\"freelinking-link\">advantage</span>&nbsp;on&nbsp;<span class=\"freelinking-link\">saving throws</span>&nbsp;against spells and other magical effects. If you have 17 or more levels in the herald class, the aura increases to a 30-foot radius.</p>",
